        <hl1>Why Not Pray?</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Sports Editor:</p>
        <p>Football teams and prayer services continue a practice nearly three millennia old. The first Olympic Games in ancient Greece were religious in nature, and never took place without elaborate ritual, prayer, libation and sometimes sacrifice.</p>
        <p>Kenneth Portnoy  Marblehead, Mass.</p>
      </block>
